        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><i>Melee Weapon Attack:</i> [[/r 1d20+5]]{+5} to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. <i>Hit:</i> 9 ([[/damage 1d12 + 3 type=bludgeoning]]) damage. If the target is a Large or smaller creature, it must succeed on a [[/save ability=strength dc=13]] saving throw or be pulled into the mud hulk's space and be engulfed by the mud hulk. While engulfed, the target can't breathe, has the &amp;Reference[condition=restrained] condition, and takes 6 ([[/damage 1d12 type=acid]]) damage at the start of each of its turns. When the mud hulk moves, the engulfed target moves with it. The mud hulk can have only one target engulfed at a time. While a creature is engulfed, the mud hulk can't use its Amorphous trait.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>An engulfed target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a successful save, the target escapes and enters the nearest unoccupied space.</p></div>",
